<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Our ComeCari Freight Exchange Platform</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .header { background-color: #2C3E50; padding: 20px; }
    .header h1 { color: #FFF; }
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #2980B9; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #FFF; border-radius: 5px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Our ComeCari Freight Exchange Platform</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining our platform. We're excited to have you on board and help you find the best freight exchange opportunities.</p>
      <p>To get started, please explore our platform and customize your profile to showcase your services and preferences.</p>
      <p><a href="{{product_url}}" class="button">Get Started</a></p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
      <p>Happy shipping!</p>
      <p>The Comecari Freight Exchange Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
